PHASE 1 – PROJECT PLAN
✅ Features:
Upload a resume (PDF/DOCX)

Extract key info (Name, Skills, Education, Experience)

Match with job descriptions from a dataset using embeddings

Recommend top 5 job matches

Web UI using Streamlit

TECH STACK:
Python

spaCy (NLP entity extraction)

pdfminer.six / docx (resume parsing)

sentence-transformers (semantic similarity)

Streamlit (simple UI)

pandas, scikit-learn for job data matching
